name: Berjalan Portable Speaker Bluetooth Wireless Stereo Speakers
content:
Highlight Features:
Berjalan provides you with the best price, the best quality products and fast delivery to your hands.
Multifunction
Support TF / USB / FM / Bluetooth / AUX, hands-free mode, FM radio.
FM function
With FM function, can search for radio stations automatically.
Wireless connection
International advanced wireless chip and circuit design technology, supports all wireless devices.
Superior Sound Quality
Use high-fidelity speakers to ensure clear, bright sound.
AUX line input
Using the AUX line input, you can directly connect external devices, such as tablet PCs / TVs / cellphones.
Multiple Play modes
Support for connection in Bluetooth mode, TF card play mode, U disk paly mode, enjoy music at any time in anywhere. (Note: The TF card and U disk are not included)
Small and portable
It is mini column shape, lightweight and cute, easy to carry with, using at indoor or outdoor.
meta_description: Berjalan provides you with the best price, the best quality products and fast delivery to your hands.
meta_title: Berjalan Portable Speaker Bluetooth Wireless Stereo Speakers

name: Electro Master EM-SK-1097 5.0Litre Electric Kettle - Silver
content: The Electric Kettle has been designed for your convenience and safety. The electric kettle has a 5.0 Litre plus other amazing features such as an automatic shutdown, water level indicator which lets you adjust the amount of water placed in the teapot.
